          'If the total revenue you generate from a customer meaningfully exceeds your acquisition costs and your customers research on YouTube, the economics are typically positive. We validate this in the diagnostic. Note: Rate increases to $7,000/month starting April 30, 2026.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Do you work only with SaaS?',
        description:
          'No. We work with consulting businesses, agencies, courses, software companies, and other B2B services. As long as the economics make sense.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Do you do everything end-to-end?',
        description:
          'Yes. Strategy, scripts, editing, thumbnails, SEO, publishing, and analytics. Your team simply need to give us feedback and clear our doubts.',
      },
      {
        title: 'How fast can I expect results?',
        description:
          'Most channels begin seeing rankings and qualified traffic within 45 to 90 days, with compounding results thereafter.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Is there a long-term contract?',
        description:
          'No forced retainers. You pay monthly and review progress. We only continue when the channel shows clear traction and positive ROI.',
      },
    ]}
  />

  <!-- CTA -->
  <CallToAction
    id="book-a-diagnostic-call"
    title="Wondering if YouTube can profitably acquire customers for you?"
    subtitle="In our diagnostic, we map whether YouTube makes sense for your business. We only engage if the numbers work in your favour."
    actions={[
      {
        variant: 'primary',
        text: 'Book a diagnostic call',
        href: 'https://cal.com/gautham-8bdvdx/30min',
        target: '_blank',
        rel: 'noopener noreferrer',
      },
    ]}
  />
